\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li723\ri0\lin723\rin0\fi-360\sb240\sa240\f2\lang7177\f0\f0\fs20\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj [8]\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li723\ri0\lin723\rin0\fi-360\sb240\sa240\rtlch\af0\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs24\lang7177\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177\i0\b0 In the downstream markets, PG Bison is one of the largest South African producers of particle board and medium density fibre board (\'93MDF\'94), both of which can be upgraded with various decorative surfaces for use in kitchens, offices, furniture and shop fitt
ing manufacturing industries. PG Bison has manufacturing facilities in Piet Retief, Stellenbosch and Pietermaritzburg where it produces particle board and in Boksburg where its produces MDF.  The geographic markets for particle board and MDF are national, 
